{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 37,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الصَّافَّاتِ",
    "englishName": "As-Saaffaat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "Those drawn up in Ranks",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 182,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 3789,
        "text": "以列班者發誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3790,
        "text": "以驅策者發誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3791,
        "text": "以誦讀教誨者發誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3792,
        "text": "你們所當崇拜者，確是獨一的，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3793,
        "text": "他是天地萬物之主，是一切東方的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3794,
        "text": "我確已用文采即繁星點綴最近的天，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3795,
        "text": "我對一切叛逆的惡魔保護它，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3796,
        "text": "他們不得竊聽上界的眾天神，他們自各方被射擊，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3797,
        "text": "被驅逐，他們將受永久的刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3798,
        "text": "但竊聽一次的，燦爛的流星就追趕上他。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3799,
        "text": "你問他們吧！究竟是他們更難造呢？還是我所創造的更難造呢？我確已用黏泥創造了他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3800,
        "text": "不然！你感到驚奇，而他們卻嘲笑你。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3801,
        "text": "他們雖聞教誨，卻不覺悟。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3802,
        "text": "他們雖見蹟象，卻加以嘲笑。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3803,
        "text": "他們說：「這個只是明顯的魔術。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3804,
        "text": "難道我們死後，已變為塵土和朽骨的時候，必定復活嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3805,
        "text": "連我們的祖先，也要復活嗎？」",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3806,
        "text": "你說：「是的！你們都要卑賤地復活。」",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3807,
        "text": "才聽見一聲吶喊，他們就瞻望著，",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3808,
        "text": "他們說：「傷哉我們！這就是報應之日。」",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3809,
        "text": "這就是你們所否認的判決之日。",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3810,
        "text": "你們應當集合不義者和他們的伴侶，以及他們捨真主而崇拜的，",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3811,
        "text": "然後指示他們火獄的道路，",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3812,
        "text": "並攔住他們，因為他們的確要受審問。",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3813,
        "text": "你們怎麼不互助呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3814,
        "text": "不然！他們在今日是歸順的。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3815,
        "text": "於是他們大家走向前來，互相談論，",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3816,
        "text": "這些人說：「你們確已用權力脅迫我們。」",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3817,
        "text": "那些人說：「不然！你們自己原來不是信道者，",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3818,
        "text": "我們對你們絕無權力。不然！你們是悖逆的民眾。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3819,
        "text": "故我們應當受我們的主的判決，我們確是嘗試的。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3820,
        "text": "所以我們使你們迷誤，我們自己也確是迷誤的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3821,
        "text": "在那日，他們必定同受刑罰。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3822,
        "text": "我必定這樣對待犯罪者。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3823,
        "text": "他們確是這樣的：有人對他們說：「除真主外，絕無應受崇拜的」，他們就妄自尊大，",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3824,
        "text": "並且說：「難道我們務必要為一個狂妄的詩人，而拋棄我們的眾神靈嗎？」",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3825,
        "text": "不然！他昭示了真理，並証實了歷代的使者。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3826,
        "text": "你們必定嘗試痛苦的刑罰，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3827,
        "text": "你們只依自己的行為而受報酬。",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3828,
        "text": "惟真主的虔誠的眾僕，",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3829,
        "text": "將享受一種可知的給養——",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3830,
        "text": "各種水果，同時他們是受優待的；",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3831,
        "text": "他們在恩澤的樂園中，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3832,
        "text": "他們坐在床上，彼此相對；",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3833,
        "text": "有人以杯子在他們之間挨次傳遞，杯中滿盛醴泉，",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3834,
        "text": "顏色潔白，飲者無不稱為美味；",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3835,
        "text": "醴泉中無麻醉物，他們也不因它而酩酊；",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3836,
        "text": "他們將有不視非禮的、美目的伴侶，",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3837,
        "text": "她們彷彿被珍藏的鴕卵樣；",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3838,
        "text": "於是他們走向前來，互相談論。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3839,
        "text": "他們中有一個人說：「我有一個朋友，",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3840,
        "text": "他問我：『你確是誠信的嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3841,
        "text": "難道我們死後，已變為塵土和朽骨的時候，還必定要受報酬嗎？』」",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3842,
        "text": "他說：「你們願看他嗎？」",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3843,
        "text": "他俯視下面，就看見他在火獄的中央，",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3844,
        "text": "他說：「以真主發誓，你的確幾乎陷害了我。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3845,
        "text": "如果沒有我的主的恩惠，我必在被拘禁者之列。",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3846,
        "text": "我們不是再死的嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3847,
        "text": "唯有我們初次的死亡，而我們絕不會受懲罰嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3848,
        "text": "這確是偉大的成功，",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3849,
        "text": "工作者應當為獲得這樣的成功而工作。」",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3850,
        "text": "那是更善的款待呢？還是欑楛樹？",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3851,
        "text": "我以它為不義者的折磨。",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3852,
        "text": "它是在火獄底生長的一棵樹，",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3853,
        "text": "它的花篦，彷彿魔頭。",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3854,
        "text": "他們必定要吃那些果實，而以它充實肚腹。",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3855,
        "text": "然後他們必定要在那些果實上加飲沸水的混湯，",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3856,
        "text": "然後他們必定要歸於火獄。",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3857,
        "text": "他們必定會發現他們的祖先是迷誤的，",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3858,
        "text": "他們卻依著他們的蹤跡而奔馳。",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3859,
        "text": "在他們之前，大半的古人確已迷誤了。",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3860,
        "text": "我在他們之間，確已派遣過許多警告者。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3861,
        "text": "你看！被警告者的結局是怎樣的？",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3862,
        "text": "除非真主的純潔的僕人們。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3863,
        "text": "努哈確已向我祈禱，我是最善於應答的！",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3864,
        "text": "我拯救他和他的信徒們脫離大難。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3865,
        "text": "我只使他的子孫得以生存。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3866,
        "text": "我使他的令名，永存於後代。",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3867,
        "text": "在各民族中，都有人說：「祝努哈平安！」",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3868,
        "text": "我必定要這樣報酬行善者們。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3869,
        "text": "他確是我的信道的僕人。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3870,
        "text": "然後，我使別的人淹死。",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3871,
        "text": "他的宗派中，確有易卜拉欣。",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3872,
        "text": "當時，他帶著健全的心靈，來見他的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3873,
        "text": "當時，他對他的父親和宗族說：「你們崇拜甚麼？",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3874,
        "text": "難道你們欲捨真主而悖謬地崇拜許多神靈嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3875,
        "text": "你們對全世界的主，究竟作甚麼猜測？」",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3876,
        "text": "他看一看星宿，",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3877,
        "text": "然後說：「我勢必要害病。」",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3878,
        "text": "他們就背離了他，",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3879,
        "text": "他就俏悄地走向他們的眾神靈，他說：「你們怎麼不吃東西呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3880,
        "text": "你們怎麼不說話呢？」",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3881,
        "text": "他就悄俏地以右手打擊他們。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3882,
        "text": "眾人就急急忙忙地來看他，",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3883,
        "text": "他說：「你們崇拜自己所雕刻的偶像嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3884,
        "text": "真主創造你們，和你們的行為。」",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3885,
        "text": "他們說：「你們應當為他而修一個火爐，然後，將他投在烈火中。」",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3886,
        "text": "他們欲謀害他，而我卻使他們變成佔下風的。",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3887,
        "text": "他說：「我果然要遷移到我的主所啟示我的地方去，他將指導我。",
        "numberInSurah": 99,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3888,
        "text": "我的主呀！求你賞賜我一個善良的兒子。」",
        "numberInSurah": 100,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3889,
        "text": "我就以一個寬厚的兒童向他報喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 101,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3890,
        "text": "當他長到能幫著他操作的時候，他說：「我的小子啊！我確已夢見我宰你為犧牲。你考慮一下！你究竟有甚麼意見？」他說：「我的父親啊！請你執行你所奉的命令吧！如果真主意欲，你將發現我是堅忍的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 102,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3891,
        "text": "他們倆既已順服真主，而他使他的兒子側臥著。",
        "numberInSurah": 103,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3892,
        "text": "我喊叫說：「易卜拉欣啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 104,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3893,
        "text": "你確已証實那個夢了。」我必定要這樣報酬行善的人們。",
        "numberInSurah": 105,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3894,
        "text": "這確是明顯的考驗。",
        "numberInSurah": 106,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3895,
        "text": "我以一個偉大的犧牲贖了他。",
        "numberInSurah": 107,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3896,
        "text": "我使他的令名，永存於後代。",
        "numberInSurah": 108,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3897,
        "text": "「祝易卜拉欣平安！」",
        "numberInSurah": 109,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3898,
        "text": "我要這樣報酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 110,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3899,
        "text": "他確是我的信道的僕人，",
        "numberInSurah": 111,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3900,
        "text": "我以將為先知和善人的易司哈格向他報喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 112,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3901,
        "text": "我降福於他和易司哈格。他們倆的子孫中，將有行善者和公然自暴自棄者。",
        "numberInSurah": 113,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3902,
        "text": "我確已施恩於穆薩和哈倫。",
        "numberInSurah": 114,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3903,
        "text": "我曾使他們倆及其宗族，得免於大難。",
        "numberInSurah": 115,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3904,
        "text": "我曾援助他們，所以他們是勝利者。",
        "numberInSurah": 116,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3905,
        "text": "我授予他們倆詳明的經典，",
        "numberInSurah": 117,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3906,
        "text": "我指引他們倆正直的道路，",
        "numberInSurah": 118,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3907,
        "text": "我使他們倆的令名，永存於後代。",
        "numberInSurah": 119,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3908,
        "text": "「祝穆薩和哈倫平安！」",
        "numberInSurah": 120,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3909,
        "text": "我必定要這樣報酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 121,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3910,
        "text": "他們倆確是我的信道的僕人。",
        "numberInSurah": 122,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3911,
        "text": "易勒雅斯確是使者。",
        "numberInSurah": 123,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3912,
        "text": "當時，他對他的宗族說：「難道你們不敬畏真主嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 124,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3913,
        "text": "難道你們祈禱白耳利，而捨棄最優越的創造者——",
        "numberInSurah": 125,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3914,
        "text": "真主，你們的主，你們祖先的主嗎？」",
        "numberInSurah": 126,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3915,
        "text": "他們否認他，所以他們必定要被拘禁。",
        "numberInSurah": 127,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3916,
        "text": "惟真主的純潔的眾僕則不然。",
        "numberInSurah": 128,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3917,
        "text": "我使他的令名，永存於後代。",
        "numberInSurah": 129,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3918,
        "text": "「祝易勒雅斯平安！」",
        "numberInSurah": 130,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3919,
        "text": "我必定要這樣報酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 131,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3920,
        "text": "他確是我的信道的僕人。",
        "numberInSurah": 132,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3921,
        "text": "魯特確是使者。",
        "numberInSurah": 133,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3922,
        "text": "當時，我拯救了他，和他的全體信徒；",
        "numberInSurah": 134,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3923,
        "text": "惟有一個老婦人和其餘的人，沒有獲得拯救。",
        "numberInSurah": 135,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3924,
        "text": "然後，我毀滅了別的許多人。",
        "numberInSurah": 136,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3925,
        "text": "你們的確朝夕經過他們的遺蹟，",
        "numberInSurah": 137,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3926,
        "text": "難道你們不了解嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 138,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3927,
        "text": "優努司確是使者。",
        "numberInSurah": 139,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3928,
        "text": "當時，他逃到那只滿載的船舶上。",
        "numberInSurah": 140,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3929,
        "text": "他就拈【門龜】，他卻是失敗的，",
        "numberInSurah": 141,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3930,
        "text": "大魚就吞了他，同時，他是應受譴責的。",
        "numberInSurah": 142,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3931,
        "text": "假若他不是常讚頌真主者，",
        "numberInSurah": 143,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3932,
        "text": "他必葬身魚腹，直到世人復活之日。",
        "numberInSurah": 144,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3933,
        "text": "然後，我將他拋在旱地上，當時他是有病的。",
        "numberInSurah": 145,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3934,
        "text": "我使一棵瓠瓜，長起來遮著他。",
        "numberInSurah": 146,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3935,
        "text": "我曾派遣他去教化十多萬民眾。",
        "numberInSurah": 147,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3936,
        "text": "他們便歸信他，我使他們享樂至一定期。",
        "numberInSurah": 148,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3937,
        "text": "你問他們吧！你的主有許多女兒，他們卻有多少兒子呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 149,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3938,
        "text": "還是我曾將眾天神造成女性的，他們曾眼見我的創造呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 150,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3939,
        "text": "真的，他們因為自己的悖謬，必定要說：",
        "numberInSurah": 151,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3940,
        "text": "「真主已生育了。」他們確是說謊者。",
        "numberInSurah": 152,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3941,
        "text": "難道他不要兒子，卻要女兒嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 153,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3942,
        "text": "你們有甚麼理由？你們怎麼這樣判斷呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 154,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3943,
        "text": "你們還不覺悟嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 155,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3944,
        "text": "難道你們有一個明証嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 156,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3945,
        "text": "拿出你們的經典來吧，倘若你們是誠實的人！",
        "numberInSurah": 157,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3946,
        "text": "他們妄言他與精靈之間，有姻親關係。精靈確已知道他們將被拘禁",
        "numberInSurah": 158,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3947,
        "text": "——超絕哉真主！他是超乎他們的敘述的",
        "numberInSurah": 159,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3948,
        "text": "——惟真主的純潔的眾僕，不被拘禁。",
        "numberInSurah": 160,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3949,
        "text": "你們和你們所崇拜的，",
        "numberInSurah": 161,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3950,
        "text": "絕不能把任何人引誘去崇拜他們，",
        "numberInSurah": 162,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3951,
        "text": "除非是將入火獄的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 163,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3952,
        "text": "（眾天神說）：「我們人人都有一個指定的地位，",
        "numberInSurah": 164,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3953,
        "text": "我們必定是排班的，",
        "numberInSurah": 165,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3954,
        "text": "我們必定是讚頌真主的。」",
        "numberInSurah": 166,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3955,
        "text": "他們的確常說：",
        "numberInSurah": 167,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3956,
        "text": "「假若我們有古人所遺留的教誨，",
        "numberInSurah": 168,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3957,
        "text": "那末，我們必是真主的純潔的僕人。」",
        "numberInSurah": 169,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3958,
        "text": "他們卻不信真主，他們不久就知道了。",
        "numberInSurah": 170,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3959,
        "text": "我對我所派遣的僕人們已有約言在先了，",
        "numberInSurah": 171,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3960,
        "text": "他們必定是被援助的，",
        "numberInSurah": 172,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3961,
        "text": "我的軍隊，必定是勝利的。",
        "numberInSurah": 173,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3962,
        "text": "你暫時退避他們吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 174,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3963,
        "text": "你看著吧！他們不久就看見了。",
        "numberInSurah": 175,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3964,
        "text": "難道他們要求我的刑罰早日實現嗎？",
        "numberInSurah": 176,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3965,
        "text": "我的刑罰一旦降於他們的庭院的時候，被警告者的早晨，真惡劣呀！",
        "numberInSurah": 177,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3966,
        "text": "你暫時退避他們吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 178,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3967,
        "text": "你看著吧！他們不久就看見了。",
        "numberInSurah": 179,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3968,
        "text": "超絕哉你的主——尊榮的主宰！他是超乎他們的敘述的。",
        "numberInSurah": 180,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3969,
        "text": "祝眾使者平安！",
        "numberInSurah": 181,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3970,
        "text": "一切讚頌，全歸真主——全世界的主！",
        "numberInSurah": 182,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
